description: The SPDR S&P Global Natural Resources ETF seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the total return performance of the S&P Global Natural Resources Index (the “Index”)Seeks to provide exposure to a number of the largest market cap securities in three natural resources sectors - agriculture, energy, and metals and miningMaximum weight of each sub-index is capped at one-third of the total weight of the Index
name: SPDR S&P Global Natural Resources ETF
